title: BONUS: 'Sexual Health Is Still Taboo' - Arthur Ashe Institute Of Urban Health
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Steve Vixamar and Dr. Marilyn Fraser of the Arthur Ashe Institute of Urban Health sit down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss the importance of spreading the word about sexual health, why it is taboo today, getting tested, and more.
